  <brief_title>Probiotics and Infections in Conscripts in Military Service</brief_title>
  <official_title>Probiotic and Respiratory and Gastrointestinal Tract Infections in Finnish Military Conscripts - a Randomized and Placebo-controlled Double-blinded Study</official_title>
